WEBVTT

00:01:28.763 --> 00:01:30.486
It took medical doctors another year

00:01:30.510 --> 00:01:33.302
to be sure that it was caused
by the Zika virus,

00:01:33.326 --> 00:01:34.477
but they're now sure.

00:01:34.501 --> 00:01:37.183
And if you're a "bring on
the evidence" type,

00:01:37.207 --> 00:01:38.770
check out this publication.

00:01:39.760 --> 00:01:42.704
So where did it come from,
and how did it get here?

00:01:42.728 --> 00:01:44.037
And it is here.

00:01:44.061 --> 00:01:46.973
Like many of our viruses,
it came out of Africa,

00:01:47.441 --> 00:01:50.790
specifically the Zika forest in Uganda.

00:01:51.776 --> 00:01:56.554
Researchers at the nearby
Yellow Fever Research Institute

00:01:56.578 --> 00:02:00.864
identified an unknown virus
in a monkey in the Zika forest